In OS based during the running of program for instance ./a.out
The HDD will load it into RAM ,then from RAM processor would execute the code.Only processor can execute the code no others can perform this.

In case of OS less the execution starts directly from flash memory.
Here RAM is issued to store runtime data which button is pressed ,it is tempororily stored in RAM. processor get the code only from flash.

Role of Flsash memory : Used to stor embedded code or embedded software.
RAM                   : used to store run tie data.
processor             : used to execute embedded software.

